# ─── IMPORTANT — Firebase config files are intentionally committed ──────────────
# This is an assessment project. The firebase_options.dart, google-services.json,
# and GoogleService-Info.plist are included in version control so the evaluator
# can build and test the app without running flutterfire configure themselves.
# In a production project these would be gitignored and injected via CI/CD secrets.
#
# Files that ARE committed (not listed here, so git tracks them):
#   lib/firebase_options.dart
#   android/app/google-services.json
#   ios/Runner/GoogleService-Info.plist